Package: timer
Title: R6 Timer
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joe", "Thorley", , "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7683-4592"))
  )
Description: A simple timer as an R6 class.
    The timer has four functions: start(), stop(), reset() and elapsed().
    The elapsed() function returns the elapsed wall clock time (as opposed to CPU time)
    as an object of class lubridate::Duration.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    lubridate,
    R6
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
Encoding: UTF-8
